    dc:description "FIGURES 86–90: Variation of the male genitalia of Phaselia erika erika. 86: Holotype, from: Afghanistan, Sarobi (g. prep. 25 G. Ebert); 87: from: N Pakistan, Shandur Pass (g. prep. 0152/2021 M. Werner); 88: from: Afghanistan, Sarobi, g. prep. 0138/2021 M. Werner); 89: from: Afghanistan, Sarobi (g. prep. 0139/2021 M. Werner); 90: from: Pakistan, Chingi (g. prep. 0089/2021 M. Werner). a = genitalia capsule; b = aedeagus. Scalebar = 1 mm." ;
